            <title>[LU-18516] do not call blocking ops when !TASK_RUNNING occurs in osd-ldisk / quota path</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18516</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With a debug kernel for sanity-quota test&#160; 1i reports the following:&lt;/p&gt;
